・2018/11/07
Order API

Supports Transparency

EasyShip API 
New Support API

・2018/07/19
Order API
 Added PromiseResponseDueDate, IsEstimatedShipDateSet

・2018/02/07
Added support for tracking Amazon Imaging fees.

・2018/01/31
Finances
Added support for tracking taxes withheld using the Marketplace Facilitator tax collection model.

Orders
Added the AddressType response element to indicate commercial or residential shipping addresses, and the ProductInfo response element to indicate the total number of items that are included in the ASIN.

Added support for the Marketplace Facilitator tax collection model in the US.

・2017/11/08
Finances
Added support for the Coupons program.
※Only US and Canada

・2017/10/23
Products
Try Cach availableDate

MerchantFulfillment
・Added label customization to GetEligibleShippingServices and CreateShipment and a HazmatType parameter to CreateShipment.
Orders
・Added the TaxClassifications, TaxingRegion, CompanyLegalName, BuyerCounty, and PaymentMethodDetails elements to the Order datatype.
Product
・ActiveButTooSoonForProcessing status

Support GetEligibleShippingService, CreateShipment
